This CGRA test runner supports parallel RTL simulation and VPD generation. To run all test cases:

  make BSG_MACHINE_PATH=$TOP/bsg_manycore/machines/pod_1x1_cgra_xcel_pod CGRA_TEST=all

To run one test case (e.g., vvadd_8x8):

  make BSG_MACHINE_PATH=$TOP/bsg_manycore/machines/pod_1x1_cgra_xcel_pod CGRA_TEST=vvadd_8x8

If you want to add a new test case, copy over the test vector .dat file to under
cgra_test_vectors and rerun ./register_tests.py.
